trans-unit.source: Represents the position of the iterator to the next node in the difference between two sets of nodes.
trans-unit.target: Representa a posição do iterador para o próximo nó na diferença entre dois conjuntos de nós.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator" />.
Retorna o navegador de resultados atual.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> property is modified when the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.MoveNext%2A> method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> property to the next node and returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.HaveCurrentNode>; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> propriedade é modificada quando o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.MoveNext%2A> método define o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> propriedade para o próximo nó e retorna <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.HaveCurrentNode>; caso contrário, o <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> propriedade permanece inalterada.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> object that identifies the current node.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> que identifica o nó atual.

trans-unit.source: Positions this iterator to the next node in the union.
trans-unit.target: Posiciona este iterador para o próximo nó na união.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.NoMoreNodes> if there are no more nodes.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.NoMoreNodes> se não houver nenhuma mais nós.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.InitRightIterator> if this function initializes the right, nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.InitRightIterator> se essa função inicia à direita, aninhados iterador.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.NeedLeftNode> if the next node needs to be fetched from the left, nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.NeedLeftNode> se o próximo nó precisa ser buscada da esquerda, aninhados iterador.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.NeedRightNode> if the next node needs to be fetched from the right, nested iterator.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.NeedRightNode> se o próximo nó precisa ser buscada da direita, aninhados iterador.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.HaveCurrentNode> if the iterator's <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> property is set to the next node in the iteration.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.SetIteratorResult.HaveCurrentNode> se o iterador <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.DifferenceIterator.Current%2A> propriedade é definida para o próximo nó na iteração.
